beer.beer_name: Rare Breed: Hello Humanoid Double IPA
beer.beer_description:
Hello Humanoid. We come in peace.

This Double IPA is brewed with malted barley, wheat and maize from the friendly carbon-based life forms over at Gladfield Malt.

Following a vigorous fermentation with the California Lager strain, we beamed up a ridiculous twelve grams per litre of hops, making this Rare Breed the hoppiest ever!

APPEAR ANCE: 
Deep gold with pronounced hop haze.
AROMA: 
Grapefruit and tropical fruit, with a hint of mint and cedar.
FLAVOUR: 
Medium bodied with fruity hop flavour and firm bitterness on the finish.
MALTS: 
A blend of Gladfield malts from New Zealand, including Pilsner, Wheat, Maize and Gladiator.
HOPS: 
Sabro, Azacca, Columbus, Cascade and Fortnight.
YEAST: 
Wyeast 2112 California Lager.
